description._content: Description: Weeds. Ground cleared 15/6/06 and seedlings planted - Seedings under these conditions have not a very good chance. (Taken 26/8/06) Location: Borneo Date: 26 August 1906 ------------------------------------------------------ Description: Planting seeds in Nurseries. On the right showing shoots from germinated seeds. On the left seedlings planted 18 days previous to date of photo. (Taken 26/8/06) Location: Borneo Date: 26 August 1906 ------------------------------------------------------ Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/528.
